author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Well, hello there. Its the last Open Bar of the year, and that means a chance to look back on the highs and lows of 2025. The best, the worst, the downright confusing. Join me, MauLer, George The Giant Slayer, Vex Electronica and DarkHour for Open Bar 168.

Subscribe to George: https://www.youtube.com/@GeorgeTheGiantSlayer
Subscribe to Vex: https://www.youtube.com/@VexElectronica
Subscribe to DarkHour: https://www.youtube.com/@DarkHourYT
title: Open Bar #168 - Our Big Fat Review Of 2025

author: The Critical Drinker
description: She was once an up-and-coming starlet, made famous by the Twilight Saga and poised to become the next big A-List leading lady. But then it all fell apart in a storm of public meltdowns, affairs and box office bombs. Join me as we discover how Kristen Stewart crashed and burned.
title: Crash And Burn - The Kristen Stewart Story
